text: The canton of Ozoir-la-Ferrière is an administrative division of the Seine-et- Marne department, in northern France. It was created at the French canton reorganisation which came into effect in March 2015. Its seat is in Ozoir-la- Ferrière.Décret n° 2014-186 du 18 février 2014 portant délimitation des cantons dans le département de Seine-et-Marne It consists of the following communes: #Chevry-Cossigny #Favières #Férolles-Attilly #Ferrières-en-Brie #Gretz-Armainvilliers #Lésigny #Ozoir-la-Ferrière #Pontcarré #Servon #Tournan- en-Brie #Villeneuve-le-Comte #Villeneuve-Saint-Denis ==References== Category:Cantons of Seine-et-Marne
